OL,5, New figures show there is a spike in   
OL,6, animal cruelty during the summer and   
OL,7, the RSPCA is warning an increase in pet
OL,8, ownership, coupled with financial      
OL,9, pressures, could see this rise further.
OL,11,FThe RSPCA receives about 90,000 calls  
OL,12,Fto its cruelty line each month, but in 
OL,13,Fthe summer it rises to 134,000 a month.
OL,15,FCalls also increased by 7.9 per cent   
OL,16,Ffrom summer 2020 to summer 2021.       
OL,18,FThe charity has started a campaign to  
OL,19,Fraise funds to help the work of its    
OL,20,Frescue teams on the frontline.         
